		<title>안전자산 선호로 다시금 상승세를 보이는 금값</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/ko/analysis/market-news/gold-bulls-in-charge-investors-seek-safety</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
